Multiple award-winning Nigerian singer Kizz Daniel has revealed he would be getting married next year, though he is yet to find a partner. The Mama hitmaker who is enjoying the success of his recent single One Ticket on which he features fellow music sensation, Davido took to Twitter to lament that all his friends are married and left him behind hence he needs to also get married in 2019. He tweeted,  In times past, the singer has been linked to the petite songstress, Chidinma Ekile but the two refuted the claims that they are an item.